summary: Provides a set of PyQt5 dialog windows and UI components that enable users to connect to an MSColab server, authenticate, manage collaborative mission‑planning operations, browse and restore archived operations, merge waypoints, and access help and version‑history information.
business_intent: Facilitate collaborative flight‑planning and mission‑operation workflows by offering a graphical interface for server authentication, operation creation/editing, permission handling, archiving, and synchronization across multiple users.
